name: language_html_data_url_userinfo_host_confusion
description: |
  The trusted-looking hostname appears in the userinfo portion; the actual host
  is example.invalid after the at sign. String-prefix checks and human review can
  therefore disagree with the parsed URL.
format: utf8-strip
decode-as: ascii
tags:
  - "language"
  - "html"
  - "xss-data"
  - "url-context"
  - "userinfo"
  - "host-confusion"
  - "url-validation"
---
https://trusted.invalid@example.invalid/xss-canary
